{"tid":581264,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"需求疲弱　iPhone X美國營運商半價清貨！","createTime":"2018-03-05T07:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T09:21:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"cdc11cacfb42c940239cdc898c1a524d4d4b0375","tid":581264,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T07:49:12.000Z","msg":"03月03日(六) 18:21   <br />\n近期多間美資大行紛紛調低iPhone X今年出貨量。（Getty Images圖片）<br />\n近期多間美資大行紛紛調低iPhone X今年出貨量。（Getty Images圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，今天美國營運商Sprint向用戶提供零首期、每月20美元的18個月分期iPhone X 64 GB合約機計劃，這意味着向用戶提供50%的折扣。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，外媒PhoneArena報道，日前，摩根大通分析師Narci Chang在最新的投資報告中大幅下調了iPhone X今年上半年的出貨預期，其中第一季度iPhone X出貨量下調25%，第二季度下調44%。 <br />\n<br />\nNarci Chang在投資報告中預計，今年1月-3月，iPhone X出貨量為1500萬部，該預測較其最初的預測數字下降500萬部，降幅為25%。同時，該分析師將4-6月的iPhone X出貨預期由原先的1800萬部調整為1000萬部，降幅為44%。"},{"pid":"1f0e8d784730d7a1d14f188182c1d892868b256f","tid":581264,"uid":37688,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:08:27.000Z","msg":"sprint<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國人眼中狗也不屌既電訊商"},{"pid":"c220be70489d09c76d8716ffb82e76c53588ada6","tid":581264,"uid":172940,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:13:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4251d711585eea25b40fc20a9a8e4be8652ebe2","tid":581264,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T08:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 解鎖賣去中國咪得, 9折肯定比人掃哂"},{"pid":"7e4440b0529e52861d9739d012a0713c5c74abdb","tid":581264,"uid":73731,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"mphone 狗也不屌啦<br />\n<br />\n對自己好d，用番android"},{"pid":"e50e7c69a1a9577b5b07dd61563388226ced06e1","tid":581264,"uid":128210,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sprint<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 美國人眼中